    @dev Only callable by the new owner admin

@notice Apply transferring ownership of `_gauge`
    @param _gauge Gauge address

accept_set_admins().details: Only callable by the new owner admin

commit_set_admins(address,address).notice: Set ownership admin to `_o_admin` and emergency admin to `_e_admin`

commit_transfer_ownership(address,addres.notice: Transfer ownership for liquidity gauge `_gauge` to `new_owner`

params._gauge: Gauge which ownership is to be transferred

set_killed(address,bool).details: When killed, the gauge always yields a rate of 0 and so cannot mint MOBI

set_rewards(address,address,bytes32,addr.notice: Set the active reward contract for `_gauge`

params._reward_contract: Reward contract address. Set to ZERO_ADDRESS to disable staking.
params._reward_tokens: List of claimable tokens for this reward contract
params._sigs: Four byte selectors for staking, withdrawing and claiming, right padded with zero bytes. If the reward contract can be claimed from but does not require staking, the staking and withdraw selectors should be set to 0x00
